WEBVTT

00:00:36.286 --> 00:00:37.203
Gu-cheon!

00:00:37.287 --> 00:00:38.621
Gu-cheon!

00:00:39.789 --> 00:00:41.708
Please come to your senses.

00:00:42.292 --> 00:00:43.293
Gu-cheon!

00:00:54.804 --> 00:00:56.139
Are you all right?

00:00:59.934 --> 00:01:01.561
Gu-cheon.

00:01:49.442 --> 00:01:54.364
THE EAST PALACE

00:01:54.948 --> 00:01:59.911
So you drove out 13 court ladies' spirits in the salt storehouse?

00:02:02.956 --> 00:02:04.499
You have done well.

00:02:04.582 --> 00:02:05.625
You may withdraw.

00:02:06.126 --> 00:02:07.710
I have something to ask you.

00:02:08.628 --> 00:02:11.381
Did you have anything to do with the broken seal

00:02:11.464 --> 00:02:13.049
On the salt storehouse?

00:02:13.550 --> 00:02:15.051
You have changed,

00:02:15.135 --> 00:02:18.930
To dare ask such a thing now.

00:02:19.889 --> 00:02:21.015
But as a child,

00:02:21.516 --> 00:02:26.271
You must have seen how such words led to bloodshed upon the palace.

00:02:26.354 --> 00:02:27.939
You saw what befell your mother.

00:02:28.022 --> 00:02:30.400
"I will wipe out every last seed of the East Palace."

00:02:31.151 --> 00:02:34.154
The Most Favored Lady of the Court who died in the pond said this.

00:02:34.863 --> 00:02:36.698
She is the pond spirit, is she not?

00:02:36.781 --> 00:02:38.116
Who exactly is she?

00:02:38.199 --> 00:02:40.577
What led to her death?

00:02:43.872 --> 00:02:46.791
Are you the only one who knows of this,

00:02:46.875 --> 00:02:49.294
Or does Gu-cheon know as well?

00:02:50.753 --> 00:02:51.880
I'm the only one who knows.

00:02:57.177 --> 00:02:59.220
Do not tell him anything.

00:02:59.721 --> 00:03:03.516
To capture the pond spirit, I need to know who she was in life.

00:03:05.768 --> 00:03:08.104
I will say this one last time.

00:03:09.314 --> 00:03:11.232
Do not try to learn about the pond spirit.

00:03:11.316 --> 00:03:13.735
You can catch it without knowing its identity.

00:03:13.818 --> 00:03:16.154
Do not look further into it.

00:03:17.113 --> 00:03:20.200
Anyone who pries into shameful secrets of the palace will die.

00:03:20.283 --> 00:03:21.326
Even

00:03:22.702 --> 00:03:24.871
A child of the royal bloodline.

00:03:38.134 --> 00:03:40.053
Are you still unwell?

00:03:41.262 --> 00:03:43.514
You are healing more slowly than last time.

00:03:43.598 --> 00:03:50.063
Sending 13 spirits back to the afterlife drained my Yang energy.

00:03:50.730 --> 00:03:53.149
I will never do this again.

00:03:54.525 --> 00:03:57.487
Very well. So tell me now.

00:03:58.613 --> 00:04:00.073
Why did you strangle me?

00:04:07.914 --> 00:04:09.123
I did?

00:04:09.707 --> 00:04:11.751
Yes. You looked

00:04:12.919 --> 00:04:14.545
Just like a spirit.

00:04:26.099 --> 00:04:27.642
In the Realm of Gwi

00:04:31.521 --> 00:04:34.274
I lose Yang energy every time I fight spirits.

00:04:36.901 --> 00:04:39.279
Sometimes, I lose too much Yang energy

00:04:40.071 --> 00:04:43.241
And become like a spirit even out of the water.

00:04:45.159 --> 00:04:48.871
It means I sometimes lose control and do not know what I might do.

00:04:51.791 --> 00:04:54.294
That is why I want to leave the palace at once.

00:04:56.129 --> 00:04:57.422
And that is the reason

00:04:58.006 --> 00:05:00.258
I hate hunting spirits.

00:05:08.808 --> 00:05:09.767
Well

00:05:12.645 --> 00:05:15.273
Now that I have told you my secret,

00:05:16.566 --> 00:05:17.734
You should

00:05:18.860 --> 00:05:20.778
Tell me what is on your mind.

00:05:21.321 --> 00:05:23.781
Who is it that you want to kill in the palace?

00:05:26.075 --> 00:05:28.119
The one who killed my mother.

00:05:31.539 --> 00:05:35.418
A cursed object containing human remains was found in the salt storehouse.

00:05:36.627 --> 00:05:38.087
Since you bore only a princess,

00:05:38.171 --> 00:05:40.548
His Majesty has not set foot in your chambers.

00:05:40.631 --> 00:05:44.886
And out of jealousy, you cursed the Queen and the other concubines, did you?

00:05:45.386 --> 00:05:46.471
That is not true.

00:05:49.265 --> 00:05:53.186
That cursed object was not my doing.

00:05:53.269 --> 00:05:54.520
Enough.

00:05:54.604 --> 00:05:56.189
This is your doing.

00:05:59.192 --> 00:06:00.151
Continue.

00:06:00.234 --> 00:06:02.153
- Your Majesty! - Your Majesty!

00:06:04.614 --> 00:06:05.823
<i>It was ten years ago.</i>

00:06:06.532 --> 00:06:10.578
<i>Her Majesty the Queen Dowager</i> <i>framed my mother and drove her out.</i>

00:06:11.162 --> 00:06:12.997
Father, please help.

00:06:13.581 --> 00:06:15.792
Please stop Her Majesty the Queen Dowager.

00:06:15.875 --> 00:06:18.920
Mother and the court ladies are innocent.

00:06:19.420 --> 00:06:23.591
- It was because I heard strange things-- - Enough.

00:06:24.217 --> 00:06:26.719
I will strip your mother of her title and cast her out

00:06:26.803 --> 00:06:28.346
For burying the cursed object.

00:06:28.846 --> 00:06:30.640
That is her only way to survive.

00:06:30.723 --> 00:06:33.518
But that cursed object does not belong to Mother.

00:06:34.102 --> 00:06:38.189
The spirits in the salt storehouse said, "The serpent's cast skin killed--"

00:06:39.732 --> 00:06:41.692
Hold your tongue.

00:06:43.111 --> 00:06:47.448
Do not say that my own child hears such things.

00:06:47.532 --> 00:06:50.201
Unless you mean to disgrace the royal house.

00:06:51.327 --> 00:06:54.747
Do not tell anyone. Anyone at all.

00:06:55.706 --> 00:06:57.333
Ever.

00:07:01.546 --> 00:07:02.922
How foolish.

00:07:07.135 --> 00:07:08.803
Utterly foolish.

00:07:10.138 --> 00:07:13.391
You must always mind your words in the palace.

00:07:31.868 --> 00:07:34.620
Follow your mother and leave the palace!

00:07:38.166 --> 00:07:39.584
Father.

00:07:40.334 --> 00:07:41.627
How could you

00:07:54.348 --> 00:07:56.434
<i>After we were cast out of the palace,</i>

00:07:57.685 --> 00:07:59.770
<i>Mother was poisoned to death</i>

00:08:02.899 --> 00:08:04.942
<i>because she found the cursed object</i>

00:08:05.443 --> 00:08:07.862
<i>and came close</i> <i>to the secret of the pond spirit.</i>

00:08:09.071 --> 00:08:12.700
Someone killed my mother to protect the secret of the pond spirit.

00:08:15.453 --> 00:08:20.333
- Are you sure you should tell me this? - I cannot unravel this secret without you.

00:08:20.958 --> 00:08:22.710
I have no choice but to trust you.

00:08:23.211 --> 00:08:24.420
Good grief.

00:08:25.254 --> 00:08:26.672
What a life.

00:08:31.260 --> 00:08:32.678
You should leave now.

00:08:39.310 --> 00:08:43.231
We must uncover who the Most Favored Lady of the Court really is. Get ready.

00:08:51.656 --> 00:08:54.200
I went to the Queen Dowager's residence to pay my respects,

00:08:54.700 --> 00:08:56.285
And I saw Saeng-gang there.

00:08:57.370 --> 00:09:00.665
She was dressed as a court lady and with a strange man.

00:09:01.165 --> 00:09:03.501
Did you give her something dangerous to do?

00:09:03.584 --> 00:09:06.087
You need not concern yourself with it.

00:09:07.380 --> 00:09:08.965
Mother,

00:09:10.049 --> 00:09:13.052
You need only concern yourself with my son.

00:09:15.888 --> 00:09:17.098
More importantly

00:09:19.267 --> 00:09:22.687
The Queen Dowager is harboring ulterior motives.

00:09:27.233 --> 00:09:29.318
It seems she intends

00:09:31.112 --> 00:09:33.864
To make the eldest son of Prince Iksang Crown Prince.

00:09:35.950 --> 00:09:37.285
In any case,

00:09:38.202 --> 00:09:41.497
We must act for the good of the royal house and the nation.

00:10:00.516 --> 00:10:05.313
You know what I had to endure to get here,

00:10:05.396 --> 00:10:07.565
And yet you say such a thing to me?

00:10:09.191 --> 00:10:12.194
Things will never go as the Queen Dowager intends.

00:10:12.278 --> 00:10:14.530
My son will inherit the throne.

00:10:14.614 --> 00:10:18.451
Actually, I will make certain of it.

00:10:21.203 --> 00:10:22.413
Yes.

00:10:24.540 --> 00:10:27.585
Even if it means using spirits.

00:10:36.302 --> 00:10:39.639
Why did we sneak into the chambers of Lady Jang? We are not thieves.

00:10:41.891 --> 00:10:43.726
Are you some kind of saint?

00:10:45.019 --> 00:10:47.855
Lady Jang has spent her whole life beside the Queen Dowager

00:10:47.938 --> 00:10:49.815
And must know all her secrets.

00:10:50.316 --> 00:10:53.903
So I mean to scare her into spilling everything about the pond spirit.

00:10:54.945 --> 00:10:58.074
Then do it properly. What on earth are we doing?

00:10:59.200 --> 00:11:00.117
Ma'am.

00:11:00.701 --> 00:11:02.870
You are back earlier than usual.

00:11:02.953 --> 00:11:04.163
I am not feeling well.

00:11:04.246 --> 00:11:05.247
- I need rest. - There!

00:11:05.331 --> 00:11:06.540
This is bad.

00:11:10.419 --> 00:11:11.253
Wait!

00:11:16.384 --> 00:11:18.052
Who who are you?

00:11:18.552 --> 00:11:20.388
Who are you to enter without permission

00:11:22.932 --> 00:11:24.350
The pond spirit

00:11:27.311 --> 00:11:30.940
- The pond spirit is here. - Wait, are you not that feng shui master?

00:11:31.023 --> 00:11:33.109
- What are you doing here? - Quiet!

00:11:34.694 --> 00:11:36.487
- Look at these footprints on the floor. - What

00:11:39.615 --> 00:11:40.700
Is this pond mud?

00:11:40.783 --> 00:11:42.159
Leave at once!

00:11:42.243 --> 00:11:45.121
- Or I will summon the guards. - Wait. I can feel it.

00:11:45.204 --> 00:11:46.497
The pond spirit

00:11:47.039 --> 00:11:47.873
What

00:11:49.959 --> 00:11:51.001
It is the pond spirit

00:11:53.462 --> 00:11:55.923
- Hey. You should earn your keep. - You wretch!

00:11:56.006 --> 00:11:57.591
Do what you are good at. Now.

00:11:57.675 --> 00:12:00.094
- How dare you come in here! - Hey. Hurry!

00:12:00.928 --> 00:12:02.847
What do you think you are doing?

00:12:03.347 --> 00:12:06.809
How dare <i>you </i>pull something so absurd! Is anyone out there?

00:12:11.939 --> 00:12:14.233
Where is that crying coming from

00:12:14.316 --> 00:12:17.403
I will wipe out every last seed of the East Palace!

00:12:20.364 --> 00:12:23.492
The pond spirit. It is here.

00:12:23.576 --> 00:12:26.454
I told you at the Queen Dowager's residence.

00:12:27.121 --> 00:12:30.291
Won-gwi finds the one responsible for its death

00:13:05.826 --> 00:13:09.079
Namo Amitabha.

00:13:11.957 --> 00:13:13.584
Namo Amitabha.

00:13:14.168 --> 00:13:16.086
You said you were a feng shui master.

00:13:18.088 --> 00:13:20.591
Do you also know how to deal with spirits?

00:13:25.054 --> 00:13:26.555
Speaking of which

00:13:28.808 --> 00:13:30.559
That damned spirit

00:13:32.186 --> 00:13:35.189
Will come for you again.

00:13:35.773 --> 00:13:36.857
Again?

00:13:38.901 --> 00:13:40.945
Then what should I do?

00:13:41.529 --> 00:13:44.073
To keep the pond spirit away from here,

00:13:44.156 --> 00:13:48.953
I need to know who it was in life.

00:13:50.704 --> 00:13:51.997
Do not worry.

00:13:52.081 --> 00:13:54.333
You can tell him everything you know.

00:13:54.834 --> 00:13:57.169
He will keep it from Her Majesty the Queen Dowager.

00:13:57.253 --> 00:13:59.296
- He knows how to keep a secret. - What?

00:14:02.299 --> 00:14:03.300
Of course.

00:14:04.760 --> 00:14:05.761
So,

00:14:07.429 --> 00:14:09.181
Who is the pond spirit?

00:14:11.392 --> 00:14:13.018
The pond spirit is

00:14:18.899 --> 00:14:24.071
The last Most favored Lady of the Court to the late King.

00:14:29.326 --> 00:14:32.621
<i>A woman of the lowest birth,</i> <i>a mere maidservant,</i>

00:14:33.122 --> 00:14:35.416
<i>caught the eye of the late King.</i>

00:14:36.208 --> 00:14:40.045
<i>She received favor of His Majesty</i> <i>and even conceived.</i>

00:14:43.507 --> 00:14:46.260
<i>But it turned out</i>

00:14:47.094 --> 00:14:51.015
<i>that she was romantically involved</i> <i>with a royal guard.</i>

00:14:54.184 --> 00:14:57.021
<i>When Her Majesty the Queen Dowager</i> <i>learned of this,</i>

00:14:58.898 --> 00:15:00.566
<i>she had the royal guard tortured.</i>

00:15:00.649 --> 00:15:01.692
Hold still!

00:15:02.526 --> 00:15:05.279
<i>But he did not confess easily.</i>

00:15:07.197 --> 00:15:10.242
<i>Troops were dispatched,</i> <i>and they found evidence.</i>

00:15:11.076 --> 00:15:14.288
<i>- He eventually admitted his guilt.</i> - Go and search!

00:15:14.955 --> 00:15:16.874
The Most Favored Lady of the Court

00:15:18.500 --> 00:15:22.588
Bore the child of the royal guard, not of the late King.

00:15:23.172 --> 00:15:25.132
After enduring torture,

00:15:25.633 --> 00:15:27.509
She miscarried

00:15:28.135 --> 00:15:31.221
And died holding a grudge against the royal family.

00:15:31.722 --> 00:15:34.850
I will wipe out every last seed of the East Palace!

00:15:39.688 --> 00:15:43.442
Then what happened to her body?

00:15:45.778 --> 00:15:47.947
It was secretly taken out of the palace.

00:15:48.447 --> 00:15:50.658
A grave would never have been an option.

00:15:51.575 --> 00:15:52.826
What about her belongings?

00:15:53.869 --> 00:15:56.246
They belonged to a traitor, so they were all burned.

00:15:57.998 --> 00:16:00.459
So there is nothing left of her?

00:16:04.254 --> 00:16:06.423
I expect so. She had no family.

00:16:11.470 --> 00:16:14.932
She died by her own wrongdoing yet cursed the royal house?

00:16:16.892 --> 00:16:18.435
There must be some greater reason,

00:16:18.936 --> 00:16:21.021
Involving the shameful secrets of the palace.

00:16:23.983 --> 00:16:28.696
I will have to ask the pond spirit myself. Is there a way to summon it?

00:16:29.571 --> 00:16:30.990
And what are you going to do?

00:16:31.073 --> 00:16:33.200
There is no way to send it to the afterlife.

00:16:39.289 --> 00:16:40.624
Lady Jang said

00:16:41.291 --> 00:16:44.586
Everyone who entered the house of the royal guard met an untimely death.

00:16:44.670 --> 00:16:47.798
- Perhaps its spirit has settled there. - Exactly.

00:16:48.298 --> 00:16:51.927
There must be a reason he lingers in that house instead of passing on.

00:16:52.428 --> 00:16:55.848
Since they were lovers, the court lady may have left her belongings behind.

00:16:57.099 --> 00:16:58.976
I must go to the house of the royal guard.

00:16:59.059 --> 00:17:00.519
Have you lost your mind?

00:17:01.562 --> 00:17:04.732
- Do you want to die an untimely death? - We have no other choice.

00:17:05.441 --> 00:17:07.985
I am the only one who can leave the palace.

00:17:08.068 --> 00:17:09.862
There is a way.

00:17:10.487 --> 00:17:12.114
I can become a soul and leave.

00:17:16.201 --> 00:17:18.954
Is that even possible?

00:17:19.705 --> 00:17:21.373
Yes, but it is dangerous.

00:17:22.458 --> 00:17:24.835
If the soul drifts too far from the body

00:17:27.296 --> 00:17:29.006
It will be hard for it to return.

00:17:30.340 --> 00:17:31.341
If things go wrong,

00:17:32.801 --> 00:17:34.511
The soul may be lost

00:17:36.889 --> 00:17:38.766
And become a spirit.

00:17:41.435 --> 00:17:43.896
If that happens, I will surely become an ak-gwi.

00:17:43.979 --> 00:17:45.647
Ak-gwi?

00:17:47.232 --> 00:17:50.360
When those with heavy karma die, they become an ak-gwi.

00:17:51.403 --> 00:17:52.613
In life

00:17:56.742 --> 00:17:58.035
Are you all right?

00:18:03.749 --> 00:18:05.167
Do you see something

00:18:06.210 --> 00:18:07.753
In the well?

00:18:15.886 --> 00:18:17.805
You do not look well.

00:18:18.472 --> 00:18:20.057
If you need my Yang energy--

00:18:20.140 --> 00:18:24.478
Then you would have to hold me close and share your warmth.

00:18:24.561 --> 00:18:25.896
Can you do that for me?

00:18:28.732 --> 00:18:31.693
Never mind. I have no intention of doing that either.

00:18:32.945 --> 00:18:34.530
Then will you remain this way?

00:18:34.613 --> 00:18:36.740
No, it will get worse.

00:18:36.824 --> 00:18:38.867
Then from now on, I will accompany you

00:18:40.244 --> 00:18:41.787
To the Realm of Gwi.

00:18:41.870 --> 00:18:43.580
Two are better than one.

00:18:43.664 --> 00:18:45.124
Teach me how.

00:18:47.292 --> 00:18:48.794
Are you asking me

00:18:49.419 --> 00:18:52.172
To teach you how to die?

00:18:52.256 --> 00:18:54.925
I should find a way to help you.

00:18:55.008 --> 00:18:56.802
There is only one way.

00:18:57.928 --> 00:18:59.805
Go and tell the King

00:19:00.305 --> 00:19:03.183
That there is no way to catch the pond spirit now

00:19:03.684 --> 00:19:06.645
And that I may lose control and start killing people,

00:19:06.728 --> 00:19:08.605
So he must release me from the palace.

00:19:14.153 --> 00:19:15.070
I cannot do that.

00:19:16.321 --> 00:19:18.198
You have to find a way.

00:19:18.282 --> 00:19:22.369
Let go of the naive thought that His Majesty will release you.

00:19:27.040 --> 00:19:29.668
Then I will leave this palace in death.

00:19:35.174 --> 00:19:37.176
If I die here,

00:19:38.510 --> 00:19:40.804
I will turn into a relentless ak-gwi.

00:19:40.888 --> 00:19:42.556
And when I do

00:19:44.892 --> 00:19:47.186
I will come for the King first.

00:19:49.605 --> 00:19:50.689
How dare you

00:19:52.232 --> 00:19:54.693
Threaten to kill His Majesty.

00:19:54.776 --> 00:19:56.153
What does it matter to you?

00:19:57.154 --> 00:19:58.864
You hate the King as well.

00:19:58.947 --> 00:19:59.907
I do.

00:19:59.990 --> 00:20:01.783
Yet he is the King of this nation.

00:20:01.867 --> 00:20:04.536
All royals are the same.

00:20:05.787 --> 00:20:07.873
They use whoever they please

00:20:08.832 --> 00:20:11.585
And do not even care if people live or die.

00:20:13.962 --> 00:20:16.048
You are no different.

00:20:21.678 --> 00:20:22.679
Miss.

00:20:28.018 --> 00:20:30.479
Royal Noble Consort Sukbin Choi wishes to see you.

00:20:32.940 --> 00:20:35.150
It has been a while, Grandmother.

00:20:35.234 --> 00:20:36.902
His Majesty told me everything.

00:20:37.402 --> 00:20:41.114
How could you think of disguising yourself as a court lady to enter the palace?

00:20:41.615 --> 00:20:44.159
And what brings you to the palace, Grandmother?

00:20:44.243 --> 00:20:47.204
You hated coming to the palace more than anyone.

00:20:48.080 --> 00:20:51.500
Will you not answer my question? Same as always. You change the subject.

00:20:54.419 --> 00:20:55.671
I am exhausted.

00:20:57.464 --> 00:20:59.216
Oh dear.

00:21:03.053 --> 00:21:04.304
Saeng-gang.

00:21:05.973 --> 00:21:09.226
I hope you do not get caught up in palace strife again,

00:21:09.309 --> 00:21:11.311
As you did as a child.

00:21:13.981 --> 00:21:18.610
You are the only one who worries about me, Grandmother.

00:21:22.072 --> 00:21:24.491
After Mother and I were driven out of the palace,

00:21:25.492 --> 00:21:29.705
There was no one but you who took care of us.

00:21:30.956 --> 00:21:32.499
What is that man like?

00:21:32.582 --> 00:21:35.377
I have heard he is strange and dangerous.

00:21:37.838 --> 00:21:39.589
He may be strange,

00:21:40.299 --> 00:21:42.592
But he is the one I need most right now.

00:21:44.094 --> 00:21:45.846
And he may be dangerous

00:21:47.973 --> 00:21:50.058
But I do not mind, as we will not be friends.

00:21:53.562 --> 00:21:57.441
The palace is a place where the sane become ill,

00:21:58.108 --> 00:22:01.778
And those with darkness in their hearts become evil.

00:22:03.905 --> 00:22:05.699
So you must be careful.

00:22:16.543 --> 00:22:17.878
<i>Gu-cheon.</i>

00:22:28.805 --> 00:22:30.766
<i>You have missed me, have you not?</i>

00:22:33.352 --> 00:22:35.645
<i>Come here.</i>

00:22:54.289 --> 00:22:55.415
This is strange.

00:22:55.916 --> 00:22:59.336
People died here before. That is why the well was sealed.

00:22:59.419 --> 00:23:01.004
And another maidservant died?

00:23:01.088 --> 00:23:06.385
Earlier at dawn, a maidservant saw a man near the well while carrying wash water.

00:23:06.468 --> 00:23:08.428
- Is that so? - Yes.

00:23:08.512 --> 00:23:11.681
It was the feng shui master staying at the East Palace.

00:23:12.474 --> 00:23:14.768
Shall I send him to the State Tribunal?

00:23:14.851 --> 00:23:17.437
No. The 70th birthday of the Queen Dowager is near.

00:23:17.521 --> 00:23:19.314
This must be handled discreetly.

00:23:19.981 --> 00:23:21.608
We must not cause a disturbance.

00:23:22.109 --> 00:23:23.318
- Yes, ma'am. - Yes, ma'am.

00:23:53.432 --> 00:23:54.516
Gu-cheon.

00:24:03.150 --> 00:24:04.651
What is this bloodstain?

00:24:08.280 --> 00:24:09.614
What is this?

00:24:10.782 --> 00:24:13.243
What are you doing out at night?

00:24:13.827 --> 00:24:15.537
Whose blood is this?

00:24:16.705 --> 00:24:18.123
What do you mean "whose blood"?

00:24:20.792 --> 00:24:22.502
Are you saying I harmed someone?

00:24:26.256 --> 00:24:27.924
Then is it your blood?

00:24:29.176 --> 00:24:31.761
Where were you hurt? And why?

00:24:31.845 --> 00:24:34.222
Perhaps I had a nosebleed in my sleep.

00:24:35.807 --> 00:24:37.809
After fighting the court ladies' spirits,

00:24:38.560 --> 00:24:39.978
I barely had any strength left.

00:24:40.812 --> 00:24:43.565
Even that damned Ggeomeoksali kept draining my Yang energy.

00:24:46.943 --> 00:24:48.487
I already told you

00:24:48.570 --> 00:24:51.490
That every time I enter the Realm of Gwi, I lose my Yang energy.

00:25:20.519 --> 00:25:21.603
Prince Yeongan.

00:25:23.980 --> 00:25:25.774
You need to get your strength back.

00:25:26.274 --> 00:25:28.193
It was not this severe before,

00:25:28.693 --> 00:25:31.780
But his condition suddenly worsened.

00:26:05.313 --> 00:26:06.690
Coming back to the East Palace

00:26:08.066 --> 00:26:11.236
Reminds me of my childhood here.

00:26:12.821 --> 00:26:15.448
This place still gives me chills.

00:26:16.825 --> 00:26:19.703
What brings you here, to a place you find so chilling?

00:26:22.414 --> 00:26:24.916
How much longer do I have to wait?

00:26:25.709 --> 00:26:27.836
I came to hear your answer myself.

00:26:27.919 --> 00:26:30.255
First, please let me leave the palace.

00:26:30.338 --> 00:26:31.673
If I stay here any longer,

00:26:32.257 --> 00:26:34.801
The Yin energy of this place will kill me.

00:26:35.969 --> 00:26:37.637
If you let me leave,

00:26:37.721 --> 00:26:40.265
I will capture the pond spirit no matter what.

00:26:43.935 --> 00:26:47.105
Tomorrow is the 70th birthday banquet of the Queen Dowager.

00:26:48.565 --> 00:26:51.985
Eliminate the pond spirit and bring Prince Yeongan back to health.

00:26:52.485 --> 00:26:53.820
You have until noon tomorrow.

00:26:55.780 --> 00:26:58.325
- Your Majesty. - Your life is no concern of mine.

00:26:59.367 --> 00:27:03.246
You will not leave this palace until I die.

00:27:04.289 --> 00:27:09.836
If my son cannot walk into the banquet on his own two feet tomorrow,

00:27:09.919 --> 00:27:13.006
I will kill you and bind your soul to the palace forever.

00:27:13.089 --> 00:27:14.549
Do you understand?

00:27:15.717 --> 00:27:17.177
Do you understand?

00:27:46.706 --> 00:27:49.876
Wait, are you not the feng shui master staying in the East Palace?

00:27:50.377 --> 00:27:52.462
Why are you here? This place is for women only.

00:27:54.214 --> 00:27:55.674
- Where is she? - What?

00:27:56.383 --> 00:27:58.426
I may be young, but I am a court lady.

00:27:58.510 --> 00:28:00.095
Watch how you speak to me.

00:28:00.178 --> 00:28:01.179
This will not do.

00:28:01.262 --> 00:28:04.516
- You must help me. - What? That man dares

00:28:05.183 --> 00:28:07.852
Miss Saeng-gang gave the order. Follow me.

00:28:19.864 --> 00:28:21.074
What is he doing?

00:28:25.745 --> 00:28:27.205
What on earth are you doing?

00:28:42.554 --> 00:28:45.306
What exactly did Miss Saeng-gang order you to do?

00:28:46.057 --> 00:28:47.100
<i>Place this brass basin</i>

00:28:47.183 --> 00:28:49.436
<i>near the house of the royal guard</i> <i>in Jungchon.</i>

00:28:50.812 --> 00:28:51.896
<i>Mark my words.</i>

00:28:52.772 --> 00:28:55.024
<i>You must never spill this water.</i>

00:28:57.527 --> 00:28:59.195
<i>I have no choice but to use my blood</i>

00:29:01.197 --> 00:29:03.658
<i>become a soul,</i> <i>and seek out the royal guard.</i>

00:29:19.841 --> 00:29:21.217
What is going on?

00:29:21.801 --> 00:29:25.096
It seems the lightning struck the jujube tree.

00:29:25.180 --> 00:29:26.139
An ill omen.

00:29:26.222 --> 00:29:30.185
It is the 70th birthday of Her Majesty. What a calamity.

00:29:30.685 --> 00:29:31.603
Good heavens.

00:29:33.188 --> 00:29:35.190
Ever heard of lightning-struck jujube wood?

00:29:36.024 --> 00:29:36.941
No, I have not.

00:29:37.442 --> 00:29:40.820
More importantly, every peach tree in the palace will be gone at this rate.

00:29:41.780 --> 00:29:44.032
That is why I asked.

00:29:44.115 --> 00:29:47.327
This wood rots when it strikes a spirit, so it is utterly useless.

00:29:47.410 --> 00:29:50.497
Is lightning-struck jujube wood any different?

00:29:50.580 --> 00:29:52.624
A jujube tree struck by lightning

00:29:52.707 --> 00:29:55.168
Is sturdy and dense enough to sink as I do.

00:30:00.048 --> 00:30:03.009
<i>It drives away evil spirits.</i> <i>Perfect for striking them down.</i>

00:30:05.553 --> 00:30:06.721
<i>Heaven is on our side.</i>

00:30:16.272 --> 00:30:17.982
This man

00:30:32.705 --> 00:30:33.998
This is exhausting.

00:31:06.030 --> 00:31:07.073
You

00:31:08.074 --> 00:31:11.870
You cannot

00:31:19.544 --> 00:31:23.464
You cannot take it.

00:33:31.175 --> 00:33:32.051
Stop it!

00:33:35.221 --> 00:33:37.640
What are you trying to protect, even in death?

00:33:37.724 --> 00:33:39.183
The fault is mine.

00:33:39.767 --> 00:33:42.103
I must return it.

00:33:44.605 --> 00:33:46.899
The fault is mine.

00:33:50.570 --> 00:33:53.197
I killed her!

00:33:59.287 --> 00:34:00.997
<i>Your blood is on this sword.</i>

00:34:01.080 --> 00:34:02.040
<i>Take it.</i>

00:34:57.845 --> 00:34:59.055
I killed her.

00:35:00.306 --> 00:35:02.892
After she became a woman of the King,

00:35:02.975 --> 00:35:04.477
I framed her

00:35:05.603 --> 00:35:07.355
And betrayed her.

00:35:11.400 --> 00:35:12.985
<i>In return for doing so,</i>

00:35:13.694 --> 00:35:16.948
<i>for making a false confession,</i>

00:35:17.448 --> 00:35:18.699
<i>the Queen Dowager promised</i>

00:35:19.534 --> 00:35:24.372
<i>to spare my family from annihilation.</i>

00:35:30.419 --> 00:35:31.379
<i>She had made</i>

00:35:32.255 --> 00:35:36.217
<i>the baby's first shirt with all her heart</i>

00:35:40.263 --> 00:35:43.683
And I buried it beneath this tree.

00:35:50.022 --> 00:35:51.023
I must

00:35:51.524 --> 00:35:53.568
Protect it

00:35:53.651 --> 00:35:55.778
Until she returns.

00:35:58.948 --> 00:36:00.074
<i>I must beg</i>

00:36:01.284 --> 00:36:03.661
<i>her forgiveness.</i>

00:36:50.208 --> 00:36:51.667
What are you trying to do?

00:36:52.960 --> 00:36:54.837
Wait! Miss Saeng-gang!

00:37:03.262 --> 00:37:04.847
Gu-cheon!

00:37:07.516 --> 00:37:09.268
Is he alive?

00:37:10.770 --> 00:37:13.522
This madman entered the Realm of Gwi without the rope.

00:37:13.606 --> 00:37:15.274
I cannot even pull his soul back.

00:37:15.775 --> 00:37:16.776
Look.

00:37:16.859 --> 00:37:18.110
Where are you now?

00:37:18.194 --> 00:37:20.529
Look. Gu-cheon!

00:37:20.613 --> 00:37:22.114
Are you even on your way back?

00:37:54.689 --> 00:37:57.108
<i>If the soul drifts too far from the body,</i>

00:37:57.191 --> 00:37:58.985
<i>it will be hard for it to return.</i>

00:37:59.068 --> 00:38:04.824
- Wake up, Gu-cheon! <i>- The soul may be lost and become a spirit.</i>

00:38:06.534 --> 00:38:09.412
<i>If that happens,</i> <i>I will surely become an ak-gwi.</i>

00:38:14.500 --> 00:38:17.670
<i>I will not let you wander alone</i> <i>as a spirit.</i>

00:38:18.754 --> 00:38:21.924
<i>I will come to you.</i>

00:38:22.883 --> 00:38:24.260
<i>Please wait for me.</i>

00:38:24.927 --> 00:38:26.012
<i>Please.</i>

00:39:50.971 --> 00:39:51.806
Gu-cheon.

00:39:58.104 --> 00:39:59.647
Come here.

00:40:10.699 --> 00:40:11.617
Come here.

00:40:12.827 --> 00:40:13.911
Mother.

00:40:18.499 --> 00:40:19.458
Gu-cheon!

00:40:21.335 --> 00:40:22.753
Do not go any closer!

00:40:22.837 --> 00:40:25.005
- Gu-cheon. - Let us leave this place.

00:40:25.089 --> 00:40:27.383
That gwi-mae lures people to their deaths.

00:40:27.466 --> 00:40:29.718
- You missed me, did you not? - Gu-cheon!

00:40:30.761 --> 00:40:32.847
- Please look properly! - Come here.

00:40:35.516 --> 00:40:36.600
Mother.

00:40:37.685 --> 00:40:38.686
Gu-cheon!

00:41:09.091 --> 00:41:09.925
<i>Mother.</i>

00:41:28.068 --> 00:41:29.069
Mother.

00:41:32.823 --> 00:41:33.824
<i>Mother.</i>

00:41:37.411 --> 00:41:39.580
I died because of you.

00:41:44.752 --> 00:41:45.794
Let go of me.

00:43:00.619 --> 00:43:01.704
Gu-cheon!

00:43:10.629 --> 00:43:13.299
Then I will leave this palace in death.

00:43:15.217 --> 00:43:17.177
If I die here,

00:43:17.928 --> 00:43:20.139
I will turn into a relentless ak-gwi.

00:43:20.222 --> 00:43:21.890
And when I do

00:43:24.184 --> 00:43:26.186
I will come for the King first.

00:43:27.688 --> 00:43:28.897
Could he be

00:47:17.000 --> 00:47:20.295
Subtitle translation by: Yun-hee Jang

